{
  "stem": "20405.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I dirty all the bed all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I tried to get up to go to the bathroom and I was dirty all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the German over there, German nurses, [INAUDIBLE], they were getting me, cleaning me up and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But when I opened the eyes, I saw over there an American doctor, officer, and a German doctor, both together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is the way I got liberated, three months after.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took me-- after that, when I got stronger, after convalescence home, the German nurses was giving me a bath and food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got a shower and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was a little stronger, they sent me to Italy, Bari.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Bari, I went to Athens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Athens, I found Dario and we went to stay in the house of his aunt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- what can I say, Carol?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing, I wanted to get-- to feel good, to feel stronger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As long as they were giving me the soup or the food that I needed, and always was coming doctor German and American, not only the German.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that they killed them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know where Dario was or where my brother was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, in Athens, I learned from Dario, because Dario was with my brother, the one who's in Italy now, I got his picture, the one showing the number.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was strong-- strong like a bull.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's two, three years younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When he got liberated, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with the trucks they took them to Italy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then in Italy, all-- all of them, they were checking by doctors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when the turn of my brother came, the doctor checked him.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
